139
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,000
Neha qulbey me teqrîben hane berîmceh ye.
 
Now our South is approximately here, Berimceh.

140
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:31,000
Gundê Hisê berê dibên heye.
 
