661
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:18,000
Cemî'en ya Reb, amîn, yek giya bişîne.
 
For all of us, oh Lord, Amen, may He send it to everyone.

662
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:21,000
Hemû qenetên Kurmancan, YouTube teswîr dikin...
 
