680
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,000
Na, ew dixwîne.
 
No, he reads them.

681
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:58,000
Tû dixwînî.
 
I read them.

682
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,000
Tû dixwînî.
 
You read them.

